<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email Address</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #34a853;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #34a853;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .code {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Verify Your Email Address</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{firstName}}!</h2>
        
        <p>Thank you for signing up for TIR Browser Platform. To complete your registration, please verify your email address.</p>
        
        <p>You can verify your email in one of two ways:</p>
        
        <h3>Option 1: Click the verification button</h3>
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
        </div>
        
        <h3>Option 2: Use the verification code</h3>
        <p>If the button doesn't work, you can use this verification code:</p>
        <div class="code">{{verificationCode}}</div>
        
        <p>Enter this code in the verification page or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #34a853;">{{verificationUrl}}</p>
        
        <p><strong>Important:</strong> This verification link and code will expire in {{expiryHours}} hours for security reasons.</p>
        
        <p>If you didn't create this account, please ignore this email. Your email address will not be verified.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The TIR Browser Platform Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent to {{email}} because you signed up for TIR Browser Platform.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
